  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "chapterTitle": "佩德罗·巴拉莫",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_106714-106748",
          "range": "106714-106748",
          "rangeStart": 106714,
          "rangeEnd": 106748,
          "markText": "你走了许多日子了。苏萨娜。那时的阳光和现在一样，只是没有现在这样红，",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1686049334,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-06-06 19:02:14",
          "chapterUid": 5,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=106714&rangeEnd=106748",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=106714&rangeEnd=106748"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_61778-61843",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "61778-61843",
      "markText": "雷德里亚神父很多年后将会回忆起那个夜晚的情景。在那天夜里，硬邦邦的床使他难以入睡，迫使他走出家门。米盖尔·巴拉莫就是在那晚死去的。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=61778&rangeEnd=61843",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=61778&rangeEnd=61843"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_2833-2857",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2833-2857",
      "markText": "一群乌鸦“哑——哑——哑——”地惊叫着掠过晴空。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2833&rangeEnd=2857",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2833&rangeEnd=2857"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_4466-4481",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4466-4481",
      "markText": "佩德罗·巴拉莫已死了好多年了。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4466&rangeEnd=4481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4466&rangeEnd=4481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_3425-3462",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3425-3462",
      "markText": "我此时感到放在我衬衣口袋中母亲的那张相片在我心口阵阵发热，她好像也在出汗。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3425&rangeEnd=3462",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3425&rangeEnd=3462"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_5652-5722",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5652-5722",
      "markText": "到了那里，我的话你将会听得更清楚，我将离你更近。如果死亡有时也会发出声音的话，那么，你将会发现，我的回忆发出的声音比我死亡发出的声音更为亲近",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5652&rangeEnd=5722",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5652&rangeEnd=5722"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_394-458",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "394-458",
      "markText": "我来科马拉是因为有人对我说，我父亲住在这儿，他好像名叫佩德罗·巴拉莫。这是家母告诉我的。我向她保证，一旦她仙逝，我立即来看望他。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=394&rangeEnd=458",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=394&rangeEnd=458"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_27924-27974",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "27924-27974",
      "markText": "正当我醒来的某一时刻，我听到了一阵呼叫声，这叫喊声拖得很长，像是醉汉发出的哀号：“啊，人生不值得！”",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=27924&rangeEnd=27974",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=27924&rangeEnd=27974"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_12139-12172",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "12139-12172",
      "markText": "教堂的时钟响了起来，一声接着一声，一声又接着一声，时间仿佛在收缩。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12139&rangeEnd=12172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12139&rangeEnd=12172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_17131-17148",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "17131-17148",
      "markText": "“发生什么事了，爱杜薇海斯太太？”",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=17131&rangeEnd=17148",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=17131&rangeEnd=17148"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_5330-5382",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5330-5382",
      "markText": "我发觉她的声音中有人的气息，她口中牙齿齐全，说话时舌头在活动，两只眼睛则和生活在地球上的人们的眼睛一样。",
      "totalCount": 100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5330&rangeEnd=5382",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5330&rangeEnd=5382"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_37626-37660",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "37626-37660",
      "markText": "这样做最不好，每叹一口气就好像把自己的生命吞掉一口，人就这样完蛋了。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=37626&rangeEnd=37660",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=37626&rangeEnd=37660"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_10124-10218",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10124-10218",
      "markText": "你躲藏在几百米的高空里，躲藏在云端，躲藏在比一切都要更远更远的地方，苏萨娜。你躲在上帝那无边无际的怀抱里，躲藏在神灵的身后。你在那里，我既追不上你，也看不到你，连我的话语也传不到你的耳际。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10124&rangeEnd=10218",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10124&rangeEnd=10218"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_17_3670-3748",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "3670-3748",
      "markText": "这声音让她浑身打战，而河水还在继续涨。从远处飘来的腐臭的气味直往她湿漉漉的脸上扑，她的一对奶子不停地上下跳动着，好像马上就要开始膨胀，去做让她堕落的勾当了。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3670&rangeEnd=3748",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3670&rangeEnd=3748"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_3015-3115",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3015-3115",
      "markText": "“对，不过，这点热算不了什么，”他回答我说，“请别烦躁。到了科马拉您会觉得更热的。那个地方好像搁在炭火上一样热，也仿佛就是地狱的门口。不瞒您说，即使这么热，那里的人死后来到地狱，还得回家拿条毯子呢。”",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3015&rangeEnd=3115",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3015&rangeEnd=3115"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_41689-41726",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "41689-41726",
      "markText": "我想回去。我感到我来时留下的足迹，就像是在山丘的一片黑色中开出了一道伤口。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=41689&rangeEnd=41726",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=41689&rangeEnd=41726"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_7426-7439",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7426-7439",
      "markText": "人一累，困倦就是最好的床铺",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7426&rangeEnd=7439",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7426&rangeEnd=7439"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_9351-9371",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9351-9371",
      "markText": "“我已跟你说过，快从厕所里出来，孩子。”",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9351&rangeEnd=9371",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9351&rangeEnd=9371"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_29096-29121",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "29096-29121",
      "markText": "“可怜的爱杜薇海斯，她的亡魂大概还在受苦受难呢。”",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=29096&rangeEnd=29121",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=29096&rangeEnd=29121"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_4_3284-3329",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3284-3329",
      "markText": "可是，这样的诗意和伟大在电影里是无法想象的。在黑暗的电影院里，老年人的恋情感动不了任何人。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=36610115&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3284&rangeEnd=3329",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfa32c00722ea043dfa5824?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3284&rangeEnd=3329"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "36610115_5_8033-8064",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "8033-8064",
      "markText": "一个人想什么时候死掉，就能什么时候死掉，而不必等待上帝的安排。",
      "totalCount": 72,
